reviewText: I would buy from this seller again. I received the DVD just fine and it was as described.

Except for the last episode, which I did not like, these are enjoyable stories.  Pamela Sue Martin is beautiful, the characters colorful, and the stories move along at a good pace.  There is much atmosphere to boot.

The Nancy Drew season 1 episodes are extremely good! The mysteries are awesome and intriguing! There are 7 episodes with four on one side of the disk and 3 on the other. I love how the episodes take place in the 70's!! Pamela Sue Martin is a brilliant Nancy Drew!!! I love this!!!
